text: Eva Rönström (later Ericsson or Eriksson, 29 December 1932 – 7 October 2021) was a Swedish gymnast. She won a silver medal in the team portable apparatus event at the 1956 Summer Olympics.Eva Eriksson . Swedish Olympic CommitteeEva Rönström. sports-reference.com She was born in Stockholm, Sweden.
